    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly mint condition \u2014 an exceptional, hard-to-find example in the used car market. The exterior is flawless: the paint is deep, rich, and glossy with absolutely no scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and every panel aligns perfectly. The interior is equally impressive, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and all controls, electronics, and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The vehicle has been meticulously maintained, with service records available to verify its history. This is a turnkey purchase for a buyer who demands the very best \u2014 you will not need to invest a single dollar in repairs or cosmetic work. A rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that truly feels new.",
