    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $4,500, a price that honestly reflects its poor condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car has significant wear and issues that any prospective buyer should be aware of. Expect visible body damage including dents, scratches, and possibly rust in certain areas. The interior shows heavy use with worn or torn upholstery, damaged trim, and likely non-functional features. Mechanically, this vehicle has known problems that will require attention \u2014 it may run, but reliability cannot be guaranteed, and repairs should be anticipated. This is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle, someone seeking parts, or a mechanically inclined individual who wants a low-cost starting point. We are not representing this as a daily driver in reliable condition. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing, and factor in repair costs when evaluating the price.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained, dependable car that has been cared for and is ready for daily use. The exterior presents nicely overall, with the paint retaining a reasonable shine, though you'll notice some minor scratches and light surface wear consistent with normal use over time. There are no major dents or rust concerns. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing typical wear on the seats and high-touch areas, but nothing torn or broken. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in good working order. Tires have decent tread remaining. This is an honest, solid used car that will serve you well for everyday driving without any surprises.",
      "price": 35000.0,
